casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Peterson, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Peterson, 120 Ohio St.3d 1208, 2008-Ohio-6104.]

*1209(No. 2007-2232 Submitted October 15, 2008 Decided December 2, 2008.) Mathias H. Heck Jr., Montgomery County Prosecuting Attorney, and R. Lynn Nothstine and Carley J. Ingram, Assistant Prosecuting Attorneys, for appellant. Daniel J. O’Brien, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
